snippet.title: Drama Space
snippet.description:
Drama Space is specifically designed for keeping the world updated about the drama industry and the latest news concerning it  (on and off the screen).
                  The motive of this channelis just not to give the relevant information about the drama industry to the world but it alsoprovides informative and enjoyable videos about the upcoming movies,seasons,plays and scenes.
